looking up her skirt.

484
00:19:53,833 --> 00:19:56,583
I wish you could've seen your
face. Full-on pervy smirk.

485
00:19:56,666 --> 00:19:58,333
[YUKI]
Wait, what?

486
00:19:58,416 --> 00:20:00,166
So I knew what to do
when you grabbed me.

487
00:20:00,250 --> 00:20:03,500
I twisted your hand toward
